cdbRemoveDB            package:R4CouchDB            R Documentation

_F_u_n_c_t_i_o_n _t_o _r_e_m_o_v_e _a _d_a_t_a_b_a_s_e.

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     Removing a database means sending a http- "DELETE"- request to
     'http://cdb$serverName:cdb$port/ ...'

_U_s_a_g_e:

     cdbRemoveDB(cdb)

_A_r_g_u_m_e_n_t_s:

     cdb: The 'cdb' has to provide 'cdb$serverName', 'cdb$port' and 
          'cdb$DBName' 

_D_e_t_a_i_l_s:

     In 'cdb' maybe a entry 'cdb$delDBName' should be provided for more
     explicit deleting respectively more secure removing.

_V_a_l_u_e:

     cdb: The CouchDB answer is stored in 'cdb$res'. Any problems on
          the R side are reportet in 'cdb$error' 

_A_u_t_h_o_r(_s):

     wact.b.prot thsteinbock@web.de

_R_e_f_e_r_e_n_c_e_s:

     <URL:   http://couchdb.apache.org/       >

_S_e_e _A_l_s_o:

     'cdbMakeDB'

